    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/47f1a8dd75c95140701b37606cee7ee4.avif?t=1747769045\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mint Notes is now on Playtest! Go and try it out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/ca1bfd89dfacdf5c0ebfa5f02196c9a1.poster.avif?t=1747769045\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/ca1bfd89dfacdf5c0ebfa5f02196c9a1.webm?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/ca1bfd89dfacdf5c0ebfa5f02196c9a1.mp4?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mint Notes is a no-code, drag-and-drop design arena for game creators. Build unlimited local boards, craft custom cards from prebuilt components, and organize your ideas effortlessly. Iterate until your dream board game becomes reality—no coding, just creative action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Highly Customizable Cards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/79f86812463c71e1ec4418880a4b1d40.poster.avif?t=1747769045\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/79f86812463c71e1ec4418880a4b1d40.webm?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/79f86812463c71e1ec4418880a4b1d40.mp4?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mint Notes empowers you to bring your unique vision to life. Customize cards with images, tags, symbols, text fields, icons, types, labels, colors, badges, and more—turning each card into exactly what you need for your game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rapid Design Iteration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/e39629c97407fae92d4d1ba2f036436b.poster.avif?t=1747769045\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/e39629c97407fae92d4d1ba2f036436b.webm?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/e39629c97407fae92d4d1ba2f036436b.mp4?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch smoothly between &quot;Design Mode&quot; and &quot;Playtest Mode&quot; for fast, effective feedback. Export and import cards via CSV to quickly create batches from an existing table of contents, design layouts on other platforms, or adjust values together. With cards grouped by type using a common template, you can effortlessly apply batch changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ease of Use</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/4d52144846f3e8b58bfa7316f9af1668.poster.avif?t=1747769045\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/4d52144846f3e8b58bfa7316f9af1668.webm?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/4d52144846f3e8b58bfa7316f9af1668.mp4?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Focus on creativity, not complexity. Mint Notes offers an intuitive drag-and-drop interface complete with tooltips and visual icons. Helpful features like grouping, auto arrangement, and smart selection streamline your workflow and keep your creative momentum going.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Organize Your Ideas</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/3785869afca329ef5791475e63a4e65f.poster.avif?t=1747769045\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/3785869afca329ef5791475e63a4e65f.webm?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007420/extras/3785869afca329ef5791475e63a4e65f.mp4?t=1747769045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your entire creative process under control on unlimited local boards. Mint Notes lets you neatly arrange, manage, and refine every concept, ensuring that your path from initial idea to polished board game is as organized as it is inspiring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Component Creation</strong>: Easily create nodes, connections, cards, and groups to organize your ideas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Markdown Preview</strong>: Supports live Markdown previews for enhanced content formatting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Automated Organization</strong>: Features like auto-organizing nodes and containers for grouping components.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>High Customizability</strong>: Personalize components with colors, badges, emblems, and borders.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cards</strong>: Create customizable cards with titles, labeled text fields, and input options.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>CSV Table Import/Export</strong>: Import CSV tables into JCards, with options to override or retain original cards. Export JCards to CSV with customizable export options.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Card Game Mode</strong>: Use your Normal Mode cards to play a customizable card game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Syncing</strong>: Keep changes in sync between Normal Mode and Card Game Mode.</p></li></ul>",
